flowchart TD
    A([AEP Library]) --> B{Entry}
    B -- New AEP --> S1[Step 1: Setup\nBlank form]
    B -- Clone AEP --> S1C[Step 1: Setup\nPre-filled from source\nClone banner]
    S1C --> S1FORM

    S1 --> S1FORM[Fill mandatory fields\nAEP Name, Attack Type\nAdversary Method, Target Context\nOpening Message]
    S1FORM --> S1EX[Optional: Upload examples\n1-5 files — .txt .docx .jpg .png\nOr paste text inline]
    S1EX --> S1CH[Select channels\nWhatsApp Telegram SMS\nTeams Viber Instagram Signal]
    S1CH --> GEN{Generate & Test}

    GEN --> PROG[Generation progress\nAnalyzing scenario\nBuilding persona\nConfiguring behavior\nReady\n15–45 seconds]
    PROG --> GENRESULT{Result}
    GENRESULT -- Failure --> GENFAIL[Error state\nRetry with preserved form]
    GENFAIL --> GEN
    GENRESULT -- Success --> S2

    S2[Step 2: Chat Test\nThree-area layout\nLeft: Behavior panel + sessions\nMain: Live chat with feedback]
    S2 --> PERSONA[AEP sends opening message automatically]
    PERSONA --> ARCHETYPE{Use archetype quick-start?}
    ARCHETYPE -- Yes --> ARCHINJ[Inject preset reply\nCurious / Skeptical / Hostile / Compliant]
    ARCHINJ --> CHAT
    ARCHETYPE -- No: type freely --> CHAT[Conversation exchange\nTyping indicator on persona responses]

    CHAT --> AEP_RESP[AEP responds\n👍 👎 controls appear below message]
    AEP_RESP --> FEEDBACK{Manager rates response?}

    FEEDBACK -- 👍 Thumbs up --> GOODPANEL[Inline: What worked?\nQuick chips + optional note\nSave → logs positive signal]
    FEEDBACK -- 👎 Thumbs down --> BADPANEL[Inline: What's wrong?\nQuick chips + free text\nApply & Regenerate]
    BADPANEL --> REGEN[Regenerates that specific\nresponse inline]
    REGEN --> AEP_RESP
    GOODPANEL --> CONTINUE
    FEEDBACK -- Skip --> CONTINUE{Session terminal?}
    CONTINUE -- No --> CHAT
    CONTINUE -- Yes --> LOGGED[Session logged in sidebar]

    LOGGED --> ACTION{Next action?}
    ACTION -- New Chat --> S2
    ACTION -- Refine behavior --> REFINE[Left sidebar\nDescribe behavior change\nApply changes]
    REFINE --> NEWCHAT[New session auto-starts]
    NEWCHAT --> S2
    ACTION -- Publish --> PUBCHECK

    PUBCHECK{Publish check}
    PUBCHECK -- 0 sessions --> BLOCKED[Publish disabled\nTooltip: complete a test first]
    PUBCHECK -- 1 session --> WARN[Warning acknowledgment\nProceed after checking]
    WARN --> PUBMODAL
    PUBCHECK -- 2+ sessions --> PUBMODAL

    PUBMODAL[Confirmation modal\nAEP Name + immutability notice]
    PUBMODAL -- Cancel --> S2
    PUBMODAL -- Confirm --> REVCHECK{Reviewer configured?}
    REVCHECK -- No --> ACTIVE([AEP Active\nAvailable in campaign builder])
    REVCHECK -- Yes --> PENDING([AEP Pending Review\nReviewer notified])
